PN,39301
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773252368
OL,3,CMother who caused 'mental breakdowns'
OL,4,Cby falsely accusing 10 men of rape
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FA mother who "blighted" the lives of
OL,8,Ften men she falsely accused of rape
OL,9,Fhas been jailed.
OL,11,FStacy Sharples, from Farnworth in
OL,12,FBolton, pleaded guilty to 10 counts of
OL,13,Fperverting the course of justice after
OL,14,Fher "wicked pack of lies" prevented
OL,15,Fsome of the men from being allowed to
OL,16,Fsee their children.
OL,18,FSharples' victims told Bolton Crown
OL,19,FCourt her false allegations led to
OL,20,F"mental breakdowns" and caused one man
OL,21,Fto consider taking his own life.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/22
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773252368
OL,3,CMother who caused 'mental breakdowns'
OL,4,Cby falsely accusing 10 men of rape
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FWhile none of the ten men she falsely
OL,8,Faccused of rape were ever charged, a
OL,9,Fnumber of them spent hours in police
OL,10,Fcustody and months on bail.
OL,12,FThe Crown Prosecution Services said it
OL,13,Fwas a "conservative estimate" that
OL,14,FSharples' false allegations cost the
OL,15,Fpolice and sexual assault health
OL,16,Fservices #120,000.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/22
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773252368
OL,3,CMother who caused 'mental breakdowns'
OL,4,Cby falsely accusing 10 men of rape
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FAfter entering her guilty plea, Judge
OL,8,FNicholas Clarke KC said: "Only
OL,9,Fbelatedly by her pleas has she now
OL,10,Facknowledged that it was all a wicked
OL,11,Fpack of lies."
OL,13,FHer lawyer said that he could offer
OL,14,F"no satisfactory explanation" for her
OL,15,Fcrimes, but said there had been
OL,16,F"concerns about her mental health and
OL,17,Fintellect for a significant period".
OL,19,FSharples was sentenced to four and a
OL,20,Fhalf years in prison on Wednesday 11
OL,21,FMarch 2026.
OL,26,@sD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/22
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773252368
OL,3,CMother who caused 'mental breakdowns'
OL,4,Cby falsely accusing 10 men of rape
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FBolton Crown Court heard that after
OL,8,Fthe investigation into Sharples was
OL,9,Flaunched, she told one of her victims:
OL,10,F"They're not pressing charges. I've
OL,11,Fgot away with it yet again."
OL,13,FSpeaking outside the court, one of
OL,14,FSharples' victims Andrew Dearden said
OL,15,Fthe impact she has had on him "will
OL,16,Fstay with me for the rest of my life".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/22
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773252368
OL,3,CMother who caused 'mental breakdowns'
OL,4,Cby falsely accusing 10 men of rape
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FMr Dearden was contacted by Sharples
OL,8,Fon Plenty of Fish in February 2019.
OL,9,FThey had consensual sex, but after
OL,10,Fthey parted ways he was "bombarded"
OL,11,Fwith messages from her asking where he
OL,12,Fwas, what he was doing and if he loved
OL,13,Fher.
OL,15,FMr Dearden later agreed to meet
OL,16,FSharples in April 2019 to help her
OL,17,Fsell a TV at a Cash Generator shop.
OL,18,FWhile he was waiting outside, Sharples
OL,19,Fcalled the police and alleged that
OL,20,Fshe'd been raped by Mr Dearden the
OL,21,Fnight before.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/22
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773252368
OL,3,CMother who caused 'mental breakdowns'
OL,4,Cby falsely accusing 10 men of rape
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FPolice arrived and arrested him there.
OL,8,FHe spent eight-and-a-half hours in
OL,9,Fpolice custody before being
OL,10,Finterviewed.
OL,12,FSpeaking outside court, Mr Dearden
OL,13,Fsaid: "It's affected me massively.
OL,14,FIt's affected my day to day living,
OL,15,Fthe way I process things. It's been a
OL,16,Fscary process... This is something
OL,17,Fthat will stay with me for the rest of
OL,18,Fmy life.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/22
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773252368
OL,3,CMother who caused 'mental breakdowns'
OL,4,Cby falsely accusing 10 men of rape
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,F"If your family hear you're being
OL,8,Faccused of such a crime it's daunting
OL,9,Ffor you to even think your family
OL,10,Fwould even think something so negative
OL,11,Fof you. I was made to feel like I
OL,12,Fwasn't enough."
OL,14,FProsecuting, Mark Monaghan told the
OL,15,Fcourt that Sharples' first false
OL,16,Fallegation came six years beforehand,
OL,17,Fand resulted in her victim spending 18
OL,18,Fmonths on bail after she accused him
OL,19,Fof forcing her to perform a sex act.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/22
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773252368
OL,3,CMother who caused 'mental breakdowns'
OL,4,Cby falsely accusing 10 men of rape
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FHe had been messaging Sharples for a
OL,8,Ffew days, after being put in touch by
OL,9,Fa friend.JSharples attended his
OL,10,Ffriend's house on Boxing Day in 2013,
OL,11,Fwhere other people were also present.
OL,13,FHe said Sharples was quiet and spent
OL,14,Fmost of the time looking at her phone.
OL,16,FAfter meeting the victim on Boxing Day
OL,17,F2013, Sharples then called her brother
OL,18,Fand falsely claimed to be in danger.
OL,19,FShe told her brother and father that
OL,20,Fthe man had forced her to perform a
OL,21,Fsex act on him.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/22
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773252368
OL,3,CMother who caused 'mental breakdowns'
OL,4,Cby falsely accusing 10 men of rape
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FShe further claimed to have been
OL,8,Fattacked by nine men and threatened
OL,9,Fwith a knife.
OL,11,FMr Monaghan said her claims were a
OL,12,F"complete fabrication'" and that the
OL,13,Fvictim had no sexual contact with her
OL,14,Fat all.
OL,16,FThe victim was arrested and
OL,17,Finterviewed. Sharples refused to
OL,18,Fattend an appointment at a sexual
OL,19,Fassault referral centre.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/22
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773252368
OL,3,CMother who caused 'mental breakdowns'
OL,4,Cby falsely accusing 10 men of rape
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FOn another occasion, a separate victim
OL,8,Fmet up with Sharples after being
OL,9,Fmatched on dating website "Plenty of
OL,10,FFish."
OL,12,FShe invited him to a hostel where she
OL,13,Fwas living in Burnage on 4 February
OL,14,F2018.
OL,16,FAfter having consensual sex, he said
OL,17,Fshe made comments which made him feel
OL,18,Funcomfortable and so he left without
OL,19,Fsaying goodbye.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/22
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773252368
OL,3,CMother who caused 'mental breakdowns'
OL,4,Cby falsely accusing 10 men of rape
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FSharples then told hostel staff that
OL,8,Fsomeone had done something to her
OL,9,F"which she did not want".
OL,11,FThey called police and handed her the
OL,12,Fphone, and she claimed to have been
OL,13,Fraped. The victim was arrested and
OL,14,Fspent 17 hours in police custody
OL,15,Fbefore being interviewed. He was
OL,16,Freleased under investigation for six
OL,17,Fmonths.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/22
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773252368
OL,3,CMother who caused 'mental breakdowns'
OL,4,Cby falsely accusing 10 men of rape
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FAnother man also met Sharples through
OL,8,FPlenty of Fish in late 2018, and while
OL,9,Fthere was some sexual contact between
OL,10,Fthe pair he did not pursue it further
OL,11,Fbecause he thought she was "weird".
OL,13,FSharples asked to meet him again in
OL,14,FApril 2019. They went for a walk at a
OL,15,Freservoir and afterwards the man said
OL,16,Fhe would not drive her home but drop
OL,17,Fher off nearby.
OL,19,FMr Monaghan said Sharples was
OL,20,F"annoyed" and told him "watch what
OL,21,Fhappens now".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/22
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773252368
OL,3,CMother who caused 'mental breakdowns'
OL,4,Cby falsely accusing 10 men of rape
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FShe called 999 and accused both the
OL,8,Fman and his cousin, who was also at
OL,9,Fthe reservoir, of rape.
OL,11,FWhen the same victim bumped into
OL,12,FSharples a couple of months later,
OL,13,Fthey had a row and she ran into a
OL,14,Fnearby chip shop called 999 again,
OL,15,Falleging: "There's a guy I got done
OL,16,Ffor rape a while ago threatening to
OL,17,Fkill me."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/22
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773252368
OL,3,CMother who caused 'mental breakdowns'
OL,4,Cby falsely accusing 10 men of rape
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FThe victim then made a comment about
OL,8,Fthe police investigating Sharples, to
OL,9,Fwhich she replied: "I've been let go.
OL,10,FThey're not pressing charges. I've got
OL,11,Faway with it. Yet again."
OL,13,FAfter Sharples was arrested, she told
OL,14,Fpolice: "You need to look into my
OL,15,Fmental health. That's all I need to
OL,16,Fsay. You'll never understand, I had a
OL,17,Fs*** upbringing.
OL,19,F"I'm a ticking time bomb, you flip me
OL,20,Foff and I'll flip back."
OL,26,@qD@TOUsD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/22
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39315
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773252368
OL,3,CMother who caused 'mental breakdowns'
OL,4,Cby falsely accusing 10 men of rape
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FOne victim in an impact statement told
OL,8,Fof how he'd "moved to Sweden to
OL,9,Freevaluate my life and I wasn't part
OL,10,Fof my children's life for a few years'.
OL,12,FHe said he now struggles to approach
OL,13,Fwomen, adding: "I have a lot of hate
OL,14,Ffor that girl, I hope she gets what
OL,15,Fshe deserves, it makes me sick to my
OL,16,Fcore."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/22
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39316
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773252368
OL,3,CMother who caused 'mental breakdowns'
OL,4,Cby falsely accusing 10 men of rape
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FA number of men told in their victim
OL,8,Fimpact statements that they were
OL,9,Fprevented from seeing their children
OL,10,Fafter the allegations, were
OL,11,Fexcommunicated from their families and
OL,12,Ffriends, struggled to form any
OL,13,Fromantic relationships, and have been
OL,14,Fleft with PTSD.
OL,16,FOne man said the false allegations
OL,17,Fabout him took him to such a dark
OL,18,Fplace he thought about ending his life.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G16/22
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39317
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773252368
OL,3,CMother who caused 'mental breakdowns'
OL,4,Cby falsely accusing 10 men of rape
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FOutside Bolton Crown Court, Detective
OL,8,FSergeant Steven Gilliland said genuine
OL,9,Fvictims should not be put off of
OL,10,Fcoming forward because of Sharples'
OL,11,Factions.
OL,13,FHe said: "There's going to be somebody
OL,14,Ftoday watching this and might be
OL,15,Fthinking are the police not going to
OL,16,Fbelieve me? Are the police going to
OL,17,Fbelieve I'm making this up? That's not
OL,18,Fthe case. We will believe what you've
OL,19,Ftold us."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G17/22
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39318
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773252368
OL,3,CMother who caused 'mental breakdowns'
OL,4,Cby falsely accusing 10 men of rape
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FThe Falsely Accused Support
OL,8,FOrganisation provides support to
OL,9,Fanyone affected by false allegations,
OL,10,Fand says this case calls into question
OL,11,Fwhether defendants deserve the right
OL,12,Fto anonymity.
OL,14,FThe CEO of the organisation, Margeret
OL,15,FGardener, said: "This case is very
OL,16,Funusual and even though the men have
OL,17,Fbeen exonerated that is not the end of
OL,18,Fthe story of them. They've been named
OL,19,Fand shamed as have their families.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G18/22
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39319
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773252368
OL,3,CMother who caused 'mental breakdowns'
OL,4,Cby falsely accusing 10 men of rape
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,F"As soon as someone is accused, one
OL,8,Fbecomes the victim and looked after
OL,9,Fwhile the other becomes a perpetrator
OL,10,Fand is open to the public... so both
OL,11,Fshould be anonymised."
OL,13,FThe Falsely Accused Support
OL,14,FOrganisation says this case calls into
OL,15,Fquestion whether defendants deserve
OL,16,Fthe right to anonymity.
OL,18,FJudge Clarke said: "I take the view
OL,19,Fthat she was a sexual predator. This
OL,20,Fhas taken resources away from genuine
OL,21,Fcrime and genuine victims."
OL,26,@zD@TOU}D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G19/22
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39320
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773252368
OL,3,CMother who caused 'mental breakdowns'
OL,4,Cby falsely accusing 10 men of rape
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FDefending Sharples, Hunter Gray said
OL,8,Fthe victims in the case would be
OL,9,Fquestioning why the defendant had made
OL,10,Fthe false allegations.
OL,12,FMr Gray said: "In reality there is no
OL,13,Fsatisfactory explanation that can be
OL,14,Fgiven.
