OL,3,CMother who caused 'mental breakdowns'
OL,4,Cby falsely accusing 10 men of rape
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,F"It's not just the harm to these
OL,8,Fvictims, but genuine victims of rape
OL,9,Fare damaged, as is the wider
OL,10,Fadministration of the criminal justice
OL,11,Fsystem." He said of the defendant: "It
OL,12,Fis correct that there have been
OL,13,Fconcerns about her mental health and
OL,14,Fintellect for a significant period of
OL,15,Ftime."
OL,17,FMr Gray said that Sharples "still
OL,18,Fstruggles to accept full
OL,19,Fresponsibility" but has shown "some
OL,20,Fremorse" and "some insight".
